q 0.5 G 1 w 50 580 m 382 580 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 555 Td (You're not bad with money. Your brain works differently:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 530 Td (TIME BLINDNESS:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 516 Td (Future feels abstract. 'Future me' isn't real.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 495 Td (IMPULSIVITY:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 481 Td (See it, want it, buy it. Dopamine seeking.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 460 Td (OUT OF SIGHT:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 446 Td (If you can't SEE the money, it doesn't exist.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 425 Td (OVERWHELM:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 411 Td (Too many accounts/bills = shut down completely.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 390 Td (SHAME SPIRAL:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 376 Td (Avoiding looking at the damage makes it worse.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 355 Td (HYPERFOCUS:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 341 Td (Can spend hours researching a $20 purchase, forget rent.) Tj ET
