BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 145.44 590 Td (THE ADHD MONEY SYSTEM) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 50 580 m 382 580 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 555 Td (The 3 Principles:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 533 Td (1. AUTOMATE:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 65 517 Td (Set up auto-pay for everything possible. No willpower needed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 495 Td (2. VISUALIZE:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 65 479 Td (Use cash envelopes or visual trackers. Make money VISIBLE.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 457 Td (3. SIMPLIFY:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 65 441 Td (5 categories max. Fewer decisions = less overwhelm.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 404 Td (The 3-Account System:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 384 Td (Account 1 - BILLS:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 65 370 Td (All fixed expenses auto-pay from here. Don't touch it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 348 Td (Account 2 - SPENDING:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 65 334 Td (Your weekly 'allowance.' When it's gone, it's gone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 312 Td (Account 3 - SAVINGS:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 65 298 Td (Auto-transfer on payday. Out of sight = safe.) Tj ET

endstream
